| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4855 — Recovery Inhibition (IMNCrew)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b1666cc0-2739-5155-8b38-747ab27a9b4a"
